'From Squeak3.7beta of ''1 April 2004'' [latest update: #5905] on 16 May 2004 at 7:59:36 pm'!"Change Set:		menuItemMorphFixDate:			16 May 2004Author:			Karl RambergThis small fix put a two pixel space between the menu icons."!!MenuItemMorph methodsFor: 'layout' stamp: 'tlk 5/16/2004 19:47'!minHeight	| iconHeight |	iconHeight := self hasIcon				ifTrue: [self icon height + 2]				ifFalse: [0].	^ self fontToUse height max: iconHeight! !